{"tid":718961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極丟架！普通話男爆粗羞辱日本女球迷：X你","createTime":"2018-06-27T05:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T01:34:17.000Z","uid":141060,"like":8,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0b3f0adff39296780014dd19588e39e91a37bc1a","tid":718961,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:42:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180627/bkn-20180627123747536-0627_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180627%2Fbkn-20180627123747536-0627_00882_001.html&d=ODU92O4brtWM%2BL3wLiKwYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0cd4627b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180627/bkn-20180627123747536-0627_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180627/photo/bkn-20180627123747536-0627_00882_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180627%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180627123747536-0627_00882_001_01p.jpg&h=6848ca53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS180627-12286-14-M&amp;d=1530075416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS180627-12286-14-M%26d%3D1530075416&d=ODU92O4brtWM%2BL3wLiKwYr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=71d70635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS180627-12286-14-M&amp;d=1530075416</a><br />\n<br />\n世界盃決賽周除咗係各國球員比試球技嘅舞台，亦係全球球迷展示國民質素嘅地方，近日就有一段疑似大陸人辱罵日本女粉絲嘅影片流出，引起極大爭議。<br />\n<br />\n據報喺日本對塞內加爾嘅賽事，有一位講普通話嘅男人場外扮做訪問，對象係一位着日本波衫嘅少女，未有出鏡嘅疑似大陸男人話：「你是日本人嗎？你們今天球賽輸死，X你祖宗！輸死你小日本...」不過女球迷似乎完全聽唔明佢講乜，全程一直保持微笑，後來另一個人用英文問佢係咪日本人，呢位少女先至答「係」，影片亦隨即完結。<br />\n<br />\n影片曝光後，大部份網民都炮轟個疑似大陸男人「極丟架」，尤其中國隊連世界盃決賽周都入唔到，球迷反而走去「打嘴炮」羞辱踢得出色嘅日本。內地網民紛紛怒轟片段中辱罵日女的男子，「真丟人，一個大老爺們欺負小姑娘算啥本事」。也有人斥責男子學哥倫比亞賤男劣行，係「不懂禮義廉恥」。<br />\n<br />\n其實日本女球迷「被玩」已經唔係今屆第1次，之前有哥倫比亞人呃日本女球迷用西班牙文講「我係妓女」，而且仲拍埋片放上網，搞到哥倫比亞外交部都要出嚟道歉。日本目前喺H組排榜首， 分組賽最後一場對波蘭只要打和都可以晉級16強。"},{"pid":"a97278197e10419614fa734108347740f97151ac","tid":718961,"uid":35430,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eea70cf4889544ebd664f7a61a6a8b91c77afa7","tid":718961,"uid":161438,"like":82,"dislike":6,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"丟中國人架關我撚事？"},{"pid":"3aabbca714ad9cce358d45ab844774c2312a3ae1","tid":718961,"uid":39200,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"大陸狗梗係想屌日本妹啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ae8367912eaf49604c9c53405f09e4d0558cd5","tid":718961,"uid":112551,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"屌, 個日本妹好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好可愛"},{"pid":"749f72a013c9f7332a45b9e3a398dd5c51eb70e0","tid":718961,"uid":5006,"like":60,"dislike":4,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"5eea70cf4889544ebd664f7a61a6a8b91c77afa7","tid":718961,"uid":161438,"like":82,"dislike":6,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"丟中國人架關我撚事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"有話關你撚事？<br />\n下面夠講哥倫比亞 又關唔關你撚事呀？<br />\n死撚開啦 起到留言問關你撚事<br />\n關你老母個閪事添呀傻鳩"},{"pid":"bc7b21e2a1405c58466f31f23e0142e511d4a9c5","tid":718961,"uid":52881,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞有廉恥咪會識道歉囉<br />\n<br />\n嬴國點會認輸"},{"pid":"07c1a2bbf23f9c137059a7209db6bf8022a641e2","tid":718961,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3aabbca714ad9cce358d45ab844774c2312a3ae1","tid":718961,"uid":39200,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:52:10.000Z","msg":"大陸狗梗係想屌日本妹啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":